# CODEOWNERS — release evidence governance
# Adjust these to your GitHub org/team handles.

# Default owners
*                                   @org/repo-owners

# Policies and validator workflows require SRE + Security + Repo Owners
/policies/**                        @org/sre @org/security @org/repo-owners
/.github/workflows/**               @org/sre @org/security @org/repo-owners

# Evidence changes (optional): require SRE and Release Managers oversight
/releases/**                         @org/sre @org/release-managers

# Documentation
/docs/**                            @org/repo-owners
